FBIS3-9015 "dreeu053_c_94001" FBIS-EEU-94-053 Document Type:Daily Report 17 Mar 1994 CZECH REPUBLIC Ministry Official Condemns Zhirinovskiy Visit LD1703223394 Prague Stanice Praha Radio Network in Czech 2130 GMT 17 Mar 94 LD1703223394 Prague Stanice Praha Radio Network Language: Czech Article Type:BFN [Text] Deputy Interior Minister Martin Fendrych described as a scandal the expected arrival in Prague of Zhirinovskiy. He declared that a man who talks about us as he does has no business being here. According to him, the Interior Ministry will look very carefully whether Zhirinovskiy violates the law governing the visits of aliens.
